<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;  font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">contact și &icirc;ntrebări.</span></p>
